import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    diff = bins - item
    scores = np.zeros_like(bins)
    
    bins_without_max_capacity = np.where(bins != max_capacity)
    diff_without_max_capacity = diff[bins_without_max_capacity]
    scores[bins_without_max_capacity] = np.log(item) / (diff_without_max_capacity + 0.001)
    
    scores[diff == item] = item
    
    return scores

import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    min_capacity = np.min(bins)
    num_bins = len(bins)

    scores = np.zeros(num_bins)

    mask = (bins != max_capacity) & (bins != min_capacity)
    scores[mask] = item / (bins[mask] - item)

    scores[bins == max_capacity] = 0
    scores[bins == item] = item

    return scores

import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    scores = np.zeros_like(bins)
    max_cap = np.max(bins)
    min_cap = np.min(bins)
    scores = np.where(bins == max_cap, -np.inf, scores)
    scores = np.where(bins == min_cap, 0, scores)
    scores = np.where((bins > min_cap) & (bins < max_cap), (item - min_cap) / (item - bins), scores)
    return scores
